爱心蔬菜包里有烂菜？湖北襄阳回应了。
Loving vegetable bag with rotten vegetables? Hubei Xiangyang responded.
澎湃新闻                      。
The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
澎湃新闻记者 钟煜豪针对3月12日湖北襄阳12345政府热线接到的关于“爱心蔬菜包里有烂菜”的市民投诉，樊城区商务局在襄阳市政府网站回复称，存在的问题政府部门已经知晓，并在采取措施，将进一步加快配送速度、提升菜品质量。
In response to a complaint received by the Government Hotline No. 12345, Xiangyang, Hubei Province, on March 12, 2006, Fan City Commercial Bureau replied on the website of the Xiangyang Municipal Government that the concerned government departments were aware of the problems and were taking measures to further speed up the delivery and improve the quality of the dishes.
这名自称“住在樊城区大庆西路化纤四季厂家属院”的市民投诉称：“收到发放的17.5元的爱心蔬菜包，里面很多油菜，还有很多都烂了，分配的菜不平均不合理。
"We received a 17.5 yuan package of loving vegetables, a lot of rapeseed, and a lot of it was rotten and the food was not even and rationally distributed," said the self-styled "Fan Cheng Tai-ching West Road Chemical Fiber Four Seasons Factory.
我建议能够合理分配蔬菜，注意检查。
I suggest that vegetables be rationally distributed and checked carefully.
”樊城区商务局在回复中还表示，将进一步增派力量，及时将政府的关怀送到千家万户，“对于您反应的问题，我们已责成办事处立即进行整改”。
In its response, Fan said it would step up its efforts to deliver the government's concern to families in a timely manner. "We have instructed the office to rectify the situation immediately."
澎湃新闻注意到，近期已有多名市民致电12345反映“蔬菜包”问题。
Peng Pai news noted that a number of citizens have recently called 12345 to reflect the "vegetable bag" problem.
同在3月12日，有市民称：“我是衡庄秀雅园小区的居民，我也是孤寡老人，订购了17.5元的蔬菜包，送来的蔬菜包有上海青、白菜苔、包菜和白菜，上海青都给我配送了十几斤。
Also on March 12, a citizen said, "I am a resident of Hengzhuang Xiuya Garden District. I am also a lonely old man. I ordered 17.5 yuan vegetable bags with Shanghai green, cabbage moss, cabbage and cabbage.
我建议蔬菜包的品种多一些。
I suggest a little more vegetable packets.
”樊城区农业农村局答复指出，按照市防疫指挥部的要求，每份蔬菜套餐不少于四种蔬菜搭配，以本地（襄阳市域内）在田大宗蔬菜为主组成。
The Fancheng Agricultural and Rural Bureau replied that according to the requirements of the city epidemic prevention command, no less than four vegetable combinations per set of vegetables, mainly local (Xiangyang City area) in the field of bulk vegetables.
我区在田蔬菜以大白菜、包菜、菜苔、上海青为主，作为主要蔬菜搭配，胡萝卜、花菜、芹菜等时令蔬菜较少，作为随机搭配，随机送到各办事处，每个社区菜品尽量保持一致。
Our district in the field of vegetables to cabbage, cabbage, moss, Shanghai green as the main vegetable mix, carrots, cauliflower, celery and other seasonal vegetables, as a random mix, sent to the offices, every community food as consistent as possible.
每份蔬菜包至少4个品种，不低于26斤进行打包配送。
At least 4 varieties of vegetables per package, not less than 26 jin for packaging and distribution.
稍早前的3月9日，有市民反映道，其是樊城区前进中路社区的工作人员，辖区所有小区居民在收到政府发放的蔬菜包之后遇到了一些问题，居民反映每次送过来的蔬菜包里面的菜质量不一致，有的时候好有的时候差，菜量比较多。
Earlier on March 9, residents of Fanch Township Community Centre reported that they had encountered some problems after receiving vegetable parcels from the Government. Residents reported that the quality of vegetables in each bag delivered was inconsistent, sometimes with good or bad times and a lot of food.
小区居民建议是否可以减少蔬菜的菜量以及保证蔬菜的质量。
Community residents advise whether vegetables can be reduced and ensure the quality of vegetables.
樊城区农业农村局当时回应称，各类蔬菜经过采摘、运输、装卸、分拣、称重、打包、装车、卸车等多环节后，有出现较少折断等现象的可能，这段时间由于气温原因，部分蔬菜在塑料袋内存放时间稍长也会影响其新鲜程度。
Fancheng Agricultural and Rural Bureau responded that vegetables after picking, transportation, loading and unloading, sorting, weighing, packaging, loading, unloading, such as the emergence of a relatively small break, and other phenomena, due to temperature reasons, some vegetables in plastic bags storage time will affect its freshness.
特殊时期，请市民克服眼前的困难，对此工作多一些体谅和理解。
Special period, please overcome the immediate difficulties, more understanding and understanding of this work.
后期我们将加强监管力度，督促相关单位提高运输效率和质量保障，避免类似事件继续发生。
Later we will strengthen supervision, urging relevant units to improve transport efficiency and quality assurance, to avoid similar incidents continue to occur.
本期编辑 邢潭推荐阅读。
